There are free, 0, N15, N20, R15, R20, R25 and R30.
As mensioned in the comment of the COBRA picture, N, R means nabel and ribs respectively.
Numbers as 0, 15, 20, 25, 30 represent the angle made by two rods. '0' is N0, we    forgeted 'N' ahead of '0'.  Deg 'free' means free breathing, and rods did not compress the abdomen.
